	</table></div></li><li class="widget widget_text" id="text-3"><h3>About</h3>			<div class="textwidget"><p><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-188" title="P1010813" src="http://pink-apron.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/P1010813-200x300.jpg" alt="P1010813" width="200" height="300" /><br />
Happy 2011!  I'm Kelly, a 28-year-old cook and recent transplant to Chicago who likes to challenge her skills and her taste buds by whipping up meals that push her beyond her comfort zone.  I especially love scratch cooking with local and high quality ingredients.  I'm not afraid to fail in the kitchen because at the end of the day I'm only human.</p>
<p>Comments?  Questions?  I love getting feedback so feel free to <a href="mailto:contact@pink-apron.com">email me</a>.  If you're a company or brand interested in a partnership I would appreciate if you would read my product review policies before contacting me.</p>
</div>
